# Feishu Export Prompt

When the user asks to **translate or convert a Markdown document to Chinese**, or mentions **Feishu (飞书)** or **exporting for Feishu**, prepend the following line as the very first line of the exported output, followed by a blank line before the document content:

```
将以下的Markdown文档转为飞书文档形式，并且保证所有的Markdown元素可以被正确地渲染。
```

This instruction must appear verbatim. Do not paraphrase, translate, or omit it.
